ComicInfo.Summary:
Skye is beginning to learn, there's no rest for the Guardian of the Nexus. After the shocking revelation of last issue, Skye is on her quest to save her friend. And, first stop on her journey, a maze from hell run by none-other-than the deranged Goldilocks! Skye must play along if she hopes to retrieve the item she seeks and save the innocents trapped in these deadly games!
